                <head>Results Of The Revolution--Five New Republics</head>
                <origin>The Cleveland Plaindealer</origin>
                <commentary/>
                <excerpt/>
                <transcript/>
                <trailer/>
                <names/>
                <summary>The Cleveland Plaindealer notes that if South Carolina can secede for any
                    reason, then so can any other state. The paper sets up five different republics,
                    seceding by regions--South, Western, Central, New England and Pacific.</summary>
                <note/>
                <look/>
            </div>
