                <summary>This article lists and compares post collected ($81,600) vs. actual cost
                    ($192,210) in South Carlina, and post collected ($532,184) vs. actual cost
                    ($153,000) in Massachusetts. South Carolina creates a debt for the U. S. Post,
                    whereas Massachusetts makes a profit.</summary>
                <note/>
